e IgA-sepharose column - Sepharose, eluted at acid pH Biological Activity: Binds A. fumigatus, bacteria Nominal specificity: &#945;1-3 glucan-containing molecules Preparation: Purified IgA Mab: S1ae7 (IgM, kappa) Derivation: BALB/J mice hybridoma with specificity to Group B (1a) streptococci Source: Hybridoma grown in serum free Gibco HB medium Purification: Affinity chromatography anti-Mouse IgM-sepharose column - Sepharose, eluted at acid pH Biological Activity: Binds A. fumigatus, bacteria Nominal specificity: oligosaccharide Preparation: Purified IgM', E'* 1. Define the specificity and affinity for carbohydrate ligands');
